title: Football Focus Transfer Deadline Day Special - 01.09.2014 - 720p
description:
Football Focus Transfer Deadline Day Special
Date: Monday 1st September 2014 

Dan Walker and the Football Focus team round up all the major transfer deadline day moves, with news and reaction from around the country. After months of speculation over the future of some of the Premier League's biggest stars, top-flight clubs have until 11.00 to strengthen their squads, and invariably many transfers will only be resolved at the last minute.
